reviewText: I was looking for a full movie.

This is a combo: part movie and part documentary. I gave this DVD 5 stars because I loved it! It is true to the Word of God! I definitely recommend this DVD to all Christians and even for those who have questions concerning Saul/Paul's part in the BIBLE'
Very bad, cheap production or maybe I had great expectation about this movie especially with Hani El Roumani in it.. I wasn't able to finish it.
